Delivery Metrics
Heavy commits = commits where matched AI-attributed lines are at least half of changed lines
C1 PR reach rate = share of heavy GitHub AI commits that reached a pull request
C2 merge rate = share of heavy AI commits that later reached mainline

C3 PR merge rate = share of PR-linked heavy GitHub AI commits whose PR merged

